= Downloading OpenSlide =

OpenSlide is available under the terms of the GNU Lesser General Public License, version 2.1.

== Source ==

Source code is available for the following releases:

 * OpenSlide 3.0.2 (stable API)
   * [http://openslide.cs.cmu.edu/download/openslide-3.0.2.tar.gz]
   * [http://openslide.cs.cmu.edu/download/openslide-3.0.2.tar.xz]
 * OpenSlide Java interface 0.8.0 (still unstable API, subject to change)
   * [http://openslide.cs.cmu.edu/download/openslide-java-0.8.0.tar.gz]
   * [http://openslide.cs.cmu.edu/download/openslide-java-0.8.0.tar.xz]

