There is an OpenSlide binding for Python available at:
[http://www.osc.edu/~kerwin/pyOpenSlide/]

== Version Control ==
[http://git.or.cz/ Git] repositories for OpenSlide are available. The commands to clone are:

 * {{{git clone git://openslide.cs.cmu.edu/openslide.git}}} ([http://openslide.cs.cmu.edu/cgi-bin/gitweb.cgi?p=openslide.git;a=summary gitweb])
 * {{{git clone git://openslide.cs.cmu.edu/openslide-java.git}}} ([http://openslide.cs.cmu.edu/cgi-bin/gitweb.cgi?p=openslide-java.git;a=summary gitweb])